rows.label: tlk70000053_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Adel-sama! Laura-sama!
I'm so happy you came!

rows.label: tlk70000053_05_msg0002
rows.name:
We've all been preparing for war here.
Invidians and Gulans, Superbians and
Iirans, all working together.

rows.label: tlk70000053_05_msg0003
rows.name:
We're all doing everything
we can to work toward one
victory - one shared future.

rows.label: tlk70000053_05_msg0004
rows.name:
I wish we could always show
solidarity like this. Unified
in war and unified in peace...

rows.label: tlk70000053_05_msg0005
rows.name:
Anyway, you don't need to
worry about us! We're all
cheering for you, too.

rows.label: tlk70000053_05_msg0006
rows.name:
If... No, WHEN you get back,
we're going to throw a huge
celebration in your honor!
